  <brief_title>Simplification From Protease Inhibitors to Raltegravir</brief_title>
  <acronym>ODIS</acronym>
  <official_title>Pilot, Open-label, Randomized, Single-center Study to Asses a Simplification Strategy From Protease Inhibitors to Raltegravir: Once Daily Isentress (ODIS)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
